hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'd like to open a business account europharmacy.ca “For The Two of Us, I used my diaries, doctored a bit, even though they were so raw and angry, because I thought if I wrote it nicely, it wouldn’t be as honest as what I splurged out at the time. I think that’s what people who are distressed recognise. I often say to them: write it down and then burn it if necessary.” (To avoid hurt and conflict in the family, she has since burnt her own diaries.)
